  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Alaser
    Alaser: Alien-Laser Class - Just moves and checks for edge collisions
    Einwanderer
    Parent Class for all "Invaders".
    EinwandererOne
    This class is the class of the first kind of invader.
    EinwandererThree
    This class is the class of the third kind of invader.
    EinwandererTwo
    This class is the class of the second kind of invader.
    Plaser
    Plaser: Player-Laser Class - Just moves and checks for edge collisions
    Ship
    This class is the space-ship that the player controls and fires on the invaders with.
    SimpleActor
    This class is a dummy class to utilise blank greenfoot actors and display text on screen.
    Space
    MyWorld Class "Space".
    UpgradeUFO
    The UpgradeUFO has a change to appear every 10 seconds above the invaders - When it gets hit by the player - the player gets an upgrade
    Warp
    The Warp class appears when the player gets to a new wave and is part of the fancy animation
